---
/**
 * ScrollCue.astro
 * Indicador visual de scroll — seta animada + label.
 *
 * Posicionamento: absolute bottom-center. O ELEMENTO PAI precisa de
 * `position: relative` (ou classe `relative`) pra o absolute funcionar corretamente.
 * Exemplo: <section class="relative min-h-screen"> <ScrollCue /> </section>
 *
 * Props: nenhuma (label via slot, default "Saiba mais")
 *
 * Acessibilidade:
 *   - animate-bounce honra prefers-reduced-motion via motion-reduce:animate-none
 *     (utilitário built-in do Tailwind — nenhum CSS extra necessário)
 */
---

<div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-1 text-celestial-600 animate-bounce motion-reduce:animate-none">
  <span class="text-sm font-sans font-medium tracking-wide select-none">
    <slot>Saiba mais</slot>
  </span>
  <svg
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="24"
    height="24"
    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    fill="none"
    stroke="currentColor"
    stroke-width="2"
    stroke-linecap="round"
    stroke-linejoin="round"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
    <path d="M12 5v14" />
    <path d="m19 12-7 7-7-7" />
  </svg>
</div>
